&lt;a class=&quot;external&quot; href=&quot;http://www.britishmuseum.org/explore/highlights/highlight_objects/gr/t/group_of_knucklebone_players.aspx&quot;&gt;http://www.britishmuseum.org/explore/highlights/highlight_objects/gr/t/group_of_knucklebone_players.aspx&lt;/A&gt; (accessed December 7, 2009). Annotated by Miriam Forman-Brunell and David D. Leitao.
